We believe in fostering a strong foundation in academics, social-emotional skills, and physical well-being to inspire students to become confident, responsible, and lifelong learners.

Project-based learning to promote critical thinking and problem-solving skills.
Technology integration to enhance learning experiences and prepare students for the 21st century.

At PS 200, we strive to create a positive and supportive school culture. We foster a sense of belonging and community through school-wide events, celebrations, and initiatives.

We believe that every student deserves to feel safe, respected, and valued. Our staff is dedicated to providing a nurturing and inclusive environment where all students can thrive.

We are committed to supporting the growth of the whole student, academically, socially, emotionally, and physically. Our programs and initiatives are designed to help students develop the skills and knowledge they need to succeed in school and in lifelong learners.
